name: DPC CN Winter Tour Regional Final - 2021/2022 presented by Perfect World Esports
description:
2022 DPC 中国联赛 第一赛季季后赛（DPC China Winter Tour - Regional Final）是由完美世界电竞主办，VALVE官方指定的DOTA2全球顶级赛事。赛事成立初衷是在特殊情况下为各大赛区的顶级精英战队，提供一个晋级国际邀请赛的桥梁。来自中国联赛的4支队伍将在为期3天紧张刺激的角逐当中，根据名次获得相应的奖金和DPC积分，为通往国际邀请赛的道路铺下基石。

Organized and produced by Perfect World Esports, the 2022 DPC China Winter Tour Regional Final comes this year as part of Valve's official Dota Pro Circuit. The tournament serves as a bridge between the Leagues and the global DPC, where the Winter Tour's top 4 teams will compete in a double elimination bracket for prize money and points towards The International.
